        <span class="col-sm-2">Patrol boat</span>
        <span class="col-sm-2"><img src="/images/wholePatrol.png"></span>
        <span class="col-sm-1">2</span>
      </div>
    </p>
    <p>You take turns clicking on a grid space on your opponent's sea. The game will display on that grid space if your shot was a hit, a red square, or a miss, a blue square.</p>
    <p>The first player to sink all of their opponent's fleet wins.</p>

